{"tid":1556690,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【支那01】廿人太子站摧花　旺角揮利器兇記者　有記者被圍毆受傷","createTime":"2019-09-09T23:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T04:02:09.000Z","uid":68738,"like":129,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"654d4b1c586c658b7282c2a8776a8542895a41d9","tid":1556690,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3263954/org/4c70623db01344da60e4185fc59a3fb9.jpg/4GOpdjhXDAHkY7_UeMtxul7UXmWcVE-ed4KNpHeCjaQ?v=w960r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3263954%2Forg%2F4c70623db01344da60e4185fc59a3fb9.jpg%2F4GOpdjhXDAHkY7_UeMtxul7UXmWcVE-ed4KNpHeCjaQ%3Fv%3Dw960r16_9&h=05aa528e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8.31港鐵太子站襲擊事件後，連日來均有市民在太子站外，擺放鮮花。凌晨4時許，約有20名「大媽」及一兩名男子，到港鐵太子站外，拆除市民近日放置在站外的鮮花。及至清晨約5時，該批男女步行至碧街與洗衣街交界「連儂牆」，有人用𠝹刀及油漆鏟清除牆上的紙張。<br />\n期間一名男記者聞訊，到場了解拍攝，突遭上述多名男女追打，並在旺角道近通菜街，將該名男記者推跌圍毆，致記者手部受傷。此時，數名其他傳媒的記者到場，立即喝止，其中一名「大媽」向《香港01》記者揮舞油漆鏟，記者閃避時撞傷腳部。<br />\n<br />\n一眾狂徒隨即四散，有在場記者報警。現場消息稱，其中一名「大媽」曾截乘的士企圖離開，被記者追及，將的士截停，並交予到場警員處理。該名大媽一度被要求登上警車協助調查，據知有人曾從身上跌出一把剪刀。至於被圍毆的男記者，則向警方講述事發經過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3263964/org/f57afb07ebdc656c2be1de1fc5261e2d.jpg/IOg545gYq6fNd71WeEVMA71MI1VBNMCTF9rVsT3a1bE?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3263964%2Forg%2Ff57afb07ebdc656c2be1de1fc5261e2d.jpg%2FIOg545gYq6fNd71WeEVMA71MI1VBNMCTF9rVsT3a1bE%3Fv%3Dw960&h=c49c8685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3263971/org/e5791cf05507650615d3b7934cff3202.jpg/srPTB330rGPH6TrCyliPjiqSODdGJGYnduaDflzmg34?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3263971%2Forg%2Fe5791cf05507650615d3b7934cff3202.jpg%2FsrPTB330rGPH6TrCyliPjiqSODdGJGYnduaDflzmg34%3Fv%3Dw960&h=4df65d35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3913240795f56ca4408134a