抗爭/革命搞十年八載唔出奇<br />\n<strong>衛城革命，生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</strong><br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n0. <span style=\"color: red;\">幫襯</span>良心小店<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">抵制</span>「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全之下，<span style=\"color: red;\">免費港鐵</span>；二人同遊，一人免費<br />\n3. 夜晚<span style=\"color: red;\">十點吶喊</span>！！！連繫左鄰右里<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: red;\">每日一post</span>，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNiLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=fbcd5d15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span>，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">低消費</span>，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">做孝子救港</span>，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆</span>貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF都買美股<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會事務，做陪審員啦<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.10"},{"pid":"4fab61b3c4ea4511ed8c7f15dda780cf8f64f90f","tid":1556690,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:30:04.000Z","msg":"咁樣燒支那d維穩費<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb72fb0279e517a097088a2d7edcf9f5371cd466","tid":1556690,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:31:20.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 請南亞仔還拖啦仆街"},{"pid":"4fd9a82407eb47e0e23abb83ad929010ac8c8938","tid":1556690,"uid":169665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T01:31:32.000Z","msg":"其實每區都有<br />\n1,2點返去仲好